OL,3,CBarcelona fan travels to Exeter after
OL,4,CSt James Park mishap
OL,6,FA Barcelona fan arrived at St James
OL,7,FPark in Exeter last night (10 March)
OL,8,Fafter mixing up the stadium with the
OL,9,Fone that shares its name in Newcastle.
OL,11,FThe Spanish supporter was expecting to
OL,12,Fsee his side take on Newcastle United
OL,13,Fin the Champions League but ended up
OL,14,Fat the wrong venue.
OL,16,FHe was only made aware of his error
OL,17,Fwhen he got to the turnstiles and
OL,18,Fshowed his ticket to a staff member.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/3
