OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1773342673
OL,3,CBarcelona fan travels to Exeter after
OL,4,CSt James Park mishap
OL,6,FHis journey from London to Devon was
OL,7,Fnot a complete waste of time as Exeter
OL,8,FCity staff sorted him out a ticket for
OL,9,Ftheir game against Lincoln.
OL,11,FAdam Spencer, Supporter Experience
OL,12,FOfficer at Exeter City, said: "One of
OL,13,Four volunteers came to the office to
OL,14,Flet us know that this guy had turned
OL,15,Fup expecting to see FC Barcelona.
OL,17,F"His English wasn't great, but from
OL,18,Fwhat we could gather, he'd come from
OL,19,FLondon. My guess is he'd put St James
OL,20,FPark in his phone and then just
OL,21,Ffollowed the directions from there.
OL,26,@tD@_OU
