CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1773342673
OL,3,CBarcelona fan travels to Exeter after
OL,4,CSt James Park mishap
OL,6,F"He was pretty gutted and a bit
OL,7,Fembarrassed. So, we sorted him out a
OL,8,Fticket and he got to watch a game at
OL,9,Fthe real St James Park. He'd be
OL,10,Fwelcome back any time."
OL,12,FUnfortunately, the travelling fan
OL,13,Fdidn't get to see Exeter City win,
OL,14,Fwith the game ending 1-0 following a
OL,15,Ffirst half goal from Lincoln's Tom
OL,16,FHamer.
